{"id":7604,"date":"2016-06-17T07:00:44","date_gmt":"2016-06-17T13:00:44","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/?p=7604"},"modified":"2018-12-07T13:27:45","modified_gmt":"2018-12-07T20:27:45","slug":"cold-hardy-opuntia-cactus-flower","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/cold-hardy-opuntia-cactus-flower\/","title":{"rendered":"Amazing Cold-hardy Opuntia Cactus Flowers"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-1 nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0px;border-color:#eae9e9;border-style:solid;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-0 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\" style=\"background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\"><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-1\"><p><em>These beautiful Opuntia cactus flowers look like roses! You'd never know they came from a prickly plant if you saw them alone.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Oh my! Have you stopped to notice how gorgeous cactus flowers are??? I had seen some before but never really paid attention until I went to the Cactus Chat at Waterwise Botanicals.<\/p>\n<p>April 2016 was a pretty exciting month in the world of cactus lovers, especially those of us with freezing winters. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/waterwise-botanicals-part-1\/\">Waterwise Botanicals<\/a>\u00a0in Escondido launched a line of cold hardy cactus (which you can <a href=\"http:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/waterwise-botanicals-opuntia-cactus\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">purchase online from Mountain Crest Gardens<\/a>) with some pretty incredible flowers.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-7711\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/This-Opuntia-cactus-flower-is-incredible-Plus-it-is-cold-hardy-so-they-can-grow-just-about-anywhere.jpg\" alt=\"This Opuntia cactus flower is incredible! Plus it is cold hardy so they can grow just about anywhere!\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/This-Opuntia-cactus-flower-is-incredible-Plus-it-is-cold-hardy-so-they-can-grow-just-about-anywhere-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/This-Opuntia-cactus-flower-is-incredible-Plus-it-is-cold-hardy-so-they-can-grow-just-about-anywhere-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/This-Opuntia-cactus-flower-is-incredible-Plus-it-is-cold-hardy-so-they-can-grow-just-about-anywhere.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>I'm really excited to share these with you! Tom Jesch, the manager of Waterwise, is a die hard cactus lover and grew up in the Sierra Nevadas. He really knows his cacti too. It was a lot of fun to see all the <a href=\"http:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/waterwise-botanicals-opuntia-cactus\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">different varieties<\/a> he's collected, including the &#8216;Baby Rita' which he hybridized himself.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7610\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7610\" class=\"wp-image-7610\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Opuntia-Baby-Rita-hybrid-by-Tom-Jesch.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia Baby Rita hybrid by Tom Jesch\" width=\"585\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Opuntia-Baby-Rita-hybrid-by-Tom-Jesch-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Opuntia-Baby-Rita-hybrid-by-Tom-Jesch-700x467.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Opuntia-Baby-Rita-hybrid-by-Tom-Jesch.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7610\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Baby Rita'<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Also at this event, the lovely <a href=\"http:\/\/debraleebaldwin.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Debra Lee Baldwin<\/a> shared about her new found love of cactus, and cactus flowers. These prickly plants are slowly getting to people. They really are great!<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7712\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7712\" class=\"wp-image-7712\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/This-Opuntia-Pina-Colada-is-pretty-incredible-when-it-comes-to-cactus-flowers.jpg\" alt=\"This Opuntia Pina Colada is pretty incredible when it comes to cactus flowers!\" width=\"585\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/This-Opuntia-Pina-Colada-is-pretty-incredible-when-it-comes-to-cactus-flowers-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/This-Opuntia-Pina-Colada-is-pretty-incredible-when-it-comes-to-cactus-flowers-700x467.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/This-Opuntia-Pina-Colada-is-pretty-incredible-when-it-comes-to-cactus-flowers.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7712\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Pina Colada'<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In her talk, Debra pointed out something I hadn't thought about before. Cactus essentially come in 3 different shapes:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=cactuschat_orbs&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F120393483%2Fcactus-plant-mammillaria-gracilis%3Fref%3Dhp_rv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Spheres or orbs<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.awin1.com\/cread.php?awinaffid=233213&awinmid=6220&clickref=cactuschat_columns&p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Flisting%2F240555835%2Fpilocereus-azureus-blue-column-cactus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Columns<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"http:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/waterwise-botanicals-opuntia-cactus\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Paddles<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Mind blowing, right? I really hadn't ever put that together, but it's definitely true! Well, this cactus chat was focused primarily on <a href=\"http:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/waterwise-botanicals-opuntia-cactus\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Opuntias<\/a> which are paddle cactus.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7709\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7709\" class=\"wp-image-7709\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Pink-Frost-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-an-amazing-flower.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia Pink Frost - A cold hardy cactus with an amazing flower\" width=\"585\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Pink-Frost-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-an-amazing-flower-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Pink-Frost-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-an-amazing-flower-700x467.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Pink-Frost-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-an-amazing-flower.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7709\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Pink Frost'<\/p><\/div>\n<p>One of the people responsible for many of these amazing <a href=\"http:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/waterwise-botanicals-opuntia-cactus\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Opuntias<\/a>, with fantastic colored blooms, is Kelly Grummons of <a href=\"https:\/\/coldhardycactus.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Cold Hardy Cactus<\/a>. I had the chance to meet him and learn a little more about the cactus he's been developing.<\/p>\n<p>It's really amazing what he's been able to produce\u00a0hybridizing these plants! In the next few years you'll see some really amazing cactus on the market!<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7608\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7608\" class=\"wp-image-7608\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Kelly-Grummons-Tom-Jesch-Cassidy-Tuttle-at-Waterwise-Botanicals-Cactus-Chat-with-cold-hardy-Opuntia-cactus.jpg\" alt=\"Kelly Grummons - Tom Jesch - Cassidy Tuttle at Waterwise Botanicals Cactus Chat with cold hardy Opuntia cactus\" width=\"585\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Kelly-Grummons-Tom-Jesch-Cassidy-Tuttle-at-Waterwise-Botanicals-Cactus-Chat-with-cold-hardy-Opuntia-cactus-500x333.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Kelly-Grummons-Tom-Jesch-Cassidy-Tuttle-at-Waterwise-Botanicals-Cactus-Chat-with-cold-hardy-Opuntia-cactus-700x467.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Kelly-Grummons-Tom-Jesch-Cassidy-Tuttle-at-Waterwise-Botanicals-Cactus-Chat-with-cold-hardy-Opuntia-cactus.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7608\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kelly Grummons &#8211; Tom Jesch &#8211; Cassidy Tuttle<\/p><\/div>\n<p>All of the pots you see behind and in front of us are filled with cacti, many of which were created by Kelly.<\/p>\n<p>The really wonderful thing about <a href=\"http:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/waterwise-botanicals-opuntia-cactus\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">this line of Opuntias<\/a>, and almost all Opuntias in general, is they are cold hardy and some are even frost tolerant! I received some from Tom a few years ago and they have survived under over a foot of snow for weeks at a time.<\/p>\n<p>On the flip side, they can also tolerate pretty extreme heat and are very drought tolerant. They can go weeks without water and still look great. If you're living in a climate like most of Utah, Arizona, Nevada, etc. Opuntias\u00a0are great plants for creating a waterwise garden.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7705\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7705\" class=\"wp-image-7705\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Orange-Chiffon-A-cold-hardy-succulent-with-stunning-flowers.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia Orange Chiffon - A cold hardy succulent with stunning flowers\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Orange-Chiffon-A-cold-hardy-succulent-with-stunning-flowers-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Orange-Chiffon-A-cold-hardy-succulent-with-stunning-flowers-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Orange-Chiffon-A-cold-hardy-succulent-with-stunning-flowers.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7705\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Orange Chiffon'<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Below you'll find some of my favorite shots of cold hardy Opuntia cacti. Most of these varieties are available to <a href=\"http:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/waterwise-botanicals-opuntia-cactus\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">purchase from Mountain Crest Gardens<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/lookingsharpcactus.com\/collections\/cactus-pads-cuttings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Looking Sharp Cactus<\/a> also has a variety of cactus pads available for sale through her shop (although she does not always ship cactus pads during the summer). They aren't the same varieties you see below, but there are some great options!<\/p>\n<p>First off, my personal favorite&#8230; <a href=\"http:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/opuntia-pina-colada\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">&#8216;Pina Colada'<\/a>. This particular cactus blooms yellow with a red stripe the first day and then the flower turns pink on the second day. How crazy is that??? I'm seriously in love with it.<\/p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_7605\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7605\" class=\"wp-image-7605\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/The-beautiful-pink-and-yellow-flowers-on-an-Opuntia-Pina-Colada-cactus.jpg\" alt=\"The beautiful pink and yellow flowers on an Opuntia Pina Colada cactus\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/The-beautiful-pink-and-yellow-flowers-on-an-Opuntia-Pina-Colada-cactus-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/The-beautiful-pink-and-yellow-flowers-on-an-Opuntia-Pina-Colada-cactus-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/The-beautiful-pink-and-yellow-flowers-on-an-Opuntia-Pina-Colada-cactus.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7605\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Pina Colada'<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_7607\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7607\" class=\"wp-image-7607\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/These-stunning-flowers-are-part-of-a-cold-hardy-cactus-line.jpg\" alt=\"These stunning flowers are part of a cold hardy cactus line\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/These-stunning-flowers-are-part-of-a-cold-hardy-cactus-line-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/These-stunning-flowers-are-part-of-a-cold-hardy-cactus-line-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/These-stunning-flowers-are-part-of-a-cold-hardy-cactus-line.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7607\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Pina Colada'<\/p><\/div><\/p>\n<p>Another favorite is this Desert Skies. The pink on it is simply stunning and so vibrant. I also love how it has some hints of orange in it too. It definitely mimics the colors of a sunset.<\/p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_7713\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7713\" class=\"wp-image-7713\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Desert-Skies-Cactus-Flower.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia Desert Skies Cactus Flower\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Desert-Skies-Cactus-Flower-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Desert-Skies-Cactus-Flower-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Desert-Skies-Cactus-Flower.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7713\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Desert Skies'<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_7702\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7702\" class=\"wp-image-7702\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Desert-Skies-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-gorgeous-flower.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia Desert Skies - A cold hardy cactus with a gorgeous flower\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Desert-Skies-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-gorgeous-flower-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Desert-Skies-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-gorgeous-flower-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Desert-Skies-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-gorgeous-flower.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7702\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Desert Skies'<\/p><\/div><\/p>\n<p>The color of this Opuntia &#8216;Party Favor' was difficult to capture. It's nearly fluorescent purple and really amazing in person.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7707\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7707\" class=\"wp-image-7707\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Party-Favor-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-stunning-flower.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia Party Favor - A cold hardy cactus with a stunning flower\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Party-Favor-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-stunning-flower-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Party-Favor-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-stunning-flower-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Party-Favor-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-stunning-flower.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7707\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Party Favor'<\/p><\/div>\n<p>There was one variety not released this year, but may be released soon called Opuntia &#8216;Red Gem Miniature'. This cute little guy actually grows really well in containers, in addition to being cold hardy and having a beautiful flower.<\/p>\n<p>I was fortunate enough to get a few pads of this and I'm excited to have them in my collection. It'll be fun to see how they do in my pots over the winter!<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_7710\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7710\" class=\"wp-image-7710\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Red-Gem-Miniature-A-cold-hardy-cactus-that-does-well-in-container-gardens.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia Red Gem Miniature - A cold hardy cactus that does well in container gardens\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Red-Gem-Miniature-A-cold-hardy-cactus-that-does-well-in-container-gardens-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Red-Gem-Miniature-A-cold-hardy-cactus-that-does-well-in-container-gardens-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Red-Gem-Miniature-A-cold-hardy-cactus-that-does-well-in-container-gardens.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7710\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Red Gem Miniature'<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Here are a few others for you to enjoy as well. Isn't it amazing how beautiful these flowers are? If you didn't see them on cactus pads you'd probably think they were roses!<\/p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_7704\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7704\" class=\"wp-image-7704\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Nel-Patel-A-beautiful-cold-hardy-cactus.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia Nel Patel - A beautiful cold hardy cactus\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Nel-Patel-A-beautiful-cold-hardy-cactus-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Nel-Patel-A-beautiful-cold-hardy-cactus-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-Nel-Patel-A-beautiful-cold-hardy-cactus.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7704\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia &#8216;Nel Patel'<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_7703\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7703\" class=\"wp-image-7703\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-macrocentra-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-two-tone-flower.jpg\" alt=\"Opuntia macrocentra - A cold hardy cactus with a two tone flower\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-macrocentra-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-two-tone-flower-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-macrocentra-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-two-tone-flower-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/05\/Opuntia-macrocentra-A-cold-hardy-cactus-with-a-two-tone-flower.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7703\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Opuntia macrocentra<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_7706\" style=\"width: 595px